//                forced sleep.
//   sub-agent  — inner voice. .md in extensions/subagents/. One-shot LLM call
//                with the parent's identity context auto-injected.
//
// ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
//
// The agent's life runs as a continuous stream. WAKE and REFLECT have no
